snippet: The PGA Tour rookies Russell Henley and Scott Langley will play one more round together at the Sony Open in Honolulu, this time with a trophy and a Masters invitation at stake.
abstract: PGA Tour rookies Russell Henley and Scott Langley, who share lead at Sony Open golf tournament, will play one more round together in Honolulu, this time with trophy and Masters invitation at stake; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: The PGA Tour rookies Russell Henley and Scott Langley will play one more round together at the Sony Open in Honolulu, this time with a trophy and a Masters invitation at stake.

headline.main: Rookies Tied for Lead in Honolulu
